  "title": "CLASS 4 LORRY CRANE DRIVER CUM STOREKEEPER",
  "description": "<p><u>Job Description</u>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Operate the Vehicles &amp; crane in a safe and effective manner by observing road safety, and comply with the relevant regulations, policies, and procedures.</li>\n  <li>Responsible, proactive, and alert.</li>\n  <li>Maintain and ensure the cleanliness of company and customer's vehicles.</li>\n  <li>Ensuring the vehicle is free from dirt, dust and debris</li>\n  <li>cleaning and polishing exterior surfaces, including paint, wheels and windows</li>\n  <li>performing routine checks to ensure the vehicle is in good condition</li>\n  <li>Reporting any damage or maintenance needs to Operations Supervisor.</li>\n  <li>Maintain and ensure the cleanliness of factory including: sweeping &amp; mopping floors, cleaning &amp; sanitizing equipment and machinery, removing trash &amp; recyclables, organizing &amp; tidying workstations &amp; storage      areas, performing regular deep cleaning and disinfection of high-touch areas</li>\n  <li>Ensuring compliance with safety and health regulations</li>\n  <li>Assisting in loading/unloading.</li>\n  <li>Any other ad hoc duties.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u>Requirements</u>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess valid Class 4 driving license to drive in Singapore with clean driving records and no records on suspension.</li>\n  <li>Possess valid lorry Crane operator license</li>\n  <li>6 days a week. (Mon - Sat, 8am - 5pm)</li>\n  <li>Preferably with at least 5 years experience.</li>\n  <li>Physically fit &amp; strong.</li>\n</ul>",
